name: Soka Fleur Warung and Cafe
address: F2P8+F93, Jl. Raya Denpasar - Gilimanuk, Antap, Kec. Selemadeg Tim., Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82162, Indonesia
review 1: Cozy place. Good food. Had sweet sour squid but small portion but suits the price. Good coffee from machine. Sweet sour prawns was good too and gado-gado. Serves small Bintang beer.
review 2: Very nice place, just next of my houseüòÅ good food and good price. Even this place near the road, but they also has a good view from the back.
review 3: This place is Amazing!!! Food is delicious, presentation is gorgeous,  prices are super affordable. The people are so nice and friendly,  you can see the ocean thru the trees from your table. One of our favorites in Bali.
review 4: A quaint cafe in the middle of nowhere. The food cooked by the wifey was good. A must stop on your way from Gilimanuk to Bali.
review 5: Good food n good price. Gurame nyat nyat, capcay sedep big porsi. Hotdog big.
